question: 18 and 19 fluff!
answer:
Spring is officially in the air and that only meant one thing — cherry blossoms. Your favorite. Of course, you were nowhere near any cherry blossom trees, but you liked getting into season by bringing out every essential of yours that smelled like the pretty, pink-petaled flowers that took over the streets of Japan. From head to toe you smelled like a Sakura tree showered you with its flowers, covering you in a delicate scent that left you in a good mood.

It wasn’t just you that enjoyed the scent. It seemed like your boyfriend loved it just as much. You were getting ready to go out to the Sunday market, putting your subtle gold jewelry on, when you felt familiar arms wrap themselves around your waist. Felt Harry’s nose brush against the crook of your neck as he took a soft, gentle inhale. You giggled at the feeling. “You smell so good,” he murmured into your skin, swaying you from side to side. “Just stay here with me for a moment.”

You shook your head, but humored him for a few seconds anyway. “We’re out of fruits,” you told him. “They got the best ones.”

“Don’t need those. Got you, don’t I?” He said, sounding so serious even though you know he was smiling. “My little cherry.”

“It’s cherry blossom, and little cherry sounds like a clit,” you said, laughing louder when he digs his fingers into your sides in an attempt to tickle you. (It worked.)

“Well you certainly got one of those don’t you?” He laughed as well, burying his face into your hair this time around. It should be weird, probably, maybe, but Harry does it in this soft and gentle way that’s anything but weird. He spun you around so he could take a good look at you in your springtime colored ensemble, looking as bright and sunshiney as the sun itself. He tucked a lock of your hair behind your ear. “And your hair’s so soft…” he looked as if he was contemplating saying more, but instead he took you by the hand and lead you to your shared bed.

Harry sat down on the foot of the said bed, propping you on his solid lap. “The Sunday market can wait a little bit,” he said, persuasive as ever as his eyes zeroed in on your lips. By the slightest sheen of red on them, he knew you had on your (his) favorite strawberry lip balm. “Now c’mon, give me a kiss, please.”

question: 1 angst 💖
answer:
1. “I think we should break up.”

I’m listening to “Love you goodbye”, “Lonely” (by Taeyeon and Jong Hyun) and Breathe (by Lee Hi) to get some inspiration and it completely destroyed me. :(

It was on one of Harry’s concert, she found out that he’s cheating on her.

She’s not sure at first, she thought she was just overthinking everything because Harry is kind and friendly to everyone. But to this particular girl, Vicky, he seems too friendly.

Y/N was there on the first concert of the tour, and Vicky was there too, of course, since she’s one of the crews. She’s the kind that Harry would fall in love with, she had long blonde hair, beautiful blue eyes, and a tall and skinny figure. And Y/N? she thinks she’s just average, she had short brown hair, an average face and body. 

But she trusts Harry, since he chooses her over anyone, she must be special.

Until his second last show on tour.

She wanted to give him a surprise, since he had done so much for her, and because she misses him so much. Y/N’s not always there with him because of her job back home. And…she found out that her period never came for the past months.

When she arrived at the arena, Mitch and Sarah was shocked to see her. They talked to her for a little bit, and they seemed very nervous and seemed like they were trying to stall her from going to the backstage.

Y/N’s heart was beating fast, her instinct was telling her something’s wrong. She took a deep breath, and went to his dressing room. When she opened the door, her smile instantly fades as she saw Harry and Vicky…kissing.

His left hand was up her thighs, right hand on her waist as they were making out.

Y/N blinked her teary eyes, smiling ironically as she spoke, “What a show.”

Harry eyes shot open, and broke off the kiss. “Y/N, babe…I…”

“I think we should break up.”

Should I write a part 2 of this? 😹I feel like this is too sad.

Main masterlist | Part 2

It was on one of Harry’s concert, she found out that he’s cheating on her.

She’s not sure at first, she thought she was just overthinking everything because Harry is kind and friendly to everyone. But to this particular girl, Vicky, he seems too friendly.

Y/N was there on the first concert of the tour, and Vicky was there too, of course, since she’s one of the crews. She’s the kind that Harry would fall in love with, she had long blonde hair, beautiful blue eyes, and a tall and skinny figure. And Y/N? she thinks she’s just average, she had short brown hair, an average face and body. 

But she trusts Harry, since he chooses her over anyone, she must be special.

Until his second last show on tour.

She wanted to give him a surprise, since he had done so much for her, and because she misses him so much. Y/N’s not always there with him because of her job back home. And…she found out that her period never came for the past months.

When she arrived at the arena, Mitch and Sarah was shocked to see her. They talked to her for a little bit, and they seemed very nervous and seemed like they were trying to stall her from going to the backstage.

Y/N’s heart was beating fast, her instinct was telling her something’s wrong. She took a deep breath, and went to his dressing room. When she opened the door, her smile instantly fades as she saw Harry and Vicky…kissing.

His left hand was up her thighs, right hand on her waist as they were making out.

Y/N blinked her teary eyes, smiling ironically as she spoke, “What a show.”

Harry eyes shot open, and broke off the kiss. “Y/N, babe…I…”

“I think we should break up.”

Should I write a part 2 of this? 😹I feel like this is too sad.

Main masterlist | Part 2

summary: Perfect; Written by Harry and Louis
body:
Perfect; Written by Harry and Louis

harry: *writes perfect*

louis: how’s it going, love?

harry: it’s fine, you can go rest lou *smiles up at him*

louis: okay. goodnight, kissy?

harry: kissy *smiles up at him*

*10 minutes later*

harry: lou? lou *pouts and shakes louis’ sleeping body*

louis: yes babe?

harry: i need help *still pouting*

louis: *giggles* c’mere, let’s write it together

harry: you’d help me? aren’t you tired?

louis: never of you

harry: *blushes* can i sit on your lap, lou?

louis: ‘course.

*once they’ve finished*

harry: yay! thanks lou, you’re the best *kisses him*

louis: ofcourse i am *boops harry’s nose* do you like it?

harry: i love it, it’s perfect
